{"data":[{"date":"06:46 02/08","title":"\u201cTr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o\u201d x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Milan ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/8/trong-phao-xac-nhan-sap-den-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Rossoneri ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Milan</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Gonzalo Higuain. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecf ra 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina m\u00f9a n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro 1 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ph\u00eda c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Higuain. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2018 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 9,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a d\u00f9 Milan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 7,5 tri\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m qua khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, HLV Gennaro Gattuso kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Higuain hay ch\u01b0a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/Ket-qua-C1---Thong-ke-tran-dau-Tottenham-1-2-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc nh\u1ecf. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan sau khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi 3 b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung, Higuain \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Sky Sport r\u1eb1ng: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n, ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 5 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Argentina n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c C\u0110V AC Milan v\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Higuain t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 55 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 105 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh c\u00f9ng Bianconeri \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n gi\u00e0nh 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 Coppa Italia c\u00f9ng 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17 nh\u01b0ng thua Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chiellini-noi-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-192376.html\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sep-lon-napoli-chi-trich-ronaldo-la-hop-dong-thuong-mai-176-192360.html\">S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/roi-juventus-buffon-mien-luon-binh-luan-ve-ronaldo-176-192279.html\">R\u1eddi Juventus, Buffon mi\u1ec5n lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4951","checkdouble":"192508"},{"date":"18:08 01/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Bahrain.</h2><h2>Olympic Pakistan thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Pakistan-team-in-Bahrain-for-practice-matches.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Bahrain\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Pakistan\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i\u00a0Bahrain. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1eef t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Trung \u0110\u00f4ng \u0111ang mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Olympic Pakistan. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB c\u1ee7a Bahrain. H\u1ecd thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Budaiya Club, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Riffa SC 1-0 v\u00e0\u00a0Sitra Club 2-0, c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Al-Ahli SC.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0Jos\u00e9 Antonio Nogueira sau khi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 52 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi\u00a0d\u1eabn d\u1eaft tuy\u1ec3n QG Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD, Pakistan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Nepal. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 b\u00ed \u1ea9n v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110TQG Pakistan ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng 201 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH FIFA khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4950","checkdouble":"192493"},{"date":"22:16 01/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng tin kh\u00f4ng vui\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u ba tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 15, 17, 21/8 nh\u01b0 l\u1ecbch c\u0169, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u2018li\u1ec1n t\u00f9 t\u00ec\u2019 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 14, 16 v\u00e0 19/8. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a qu\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat b\u1edbt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Pakistan ng\u00e0y 14/8, g\u1eb7p Nepal ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u2018th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng\u2019 g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thay v\u00ec 4 ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, tr\u00e1nh r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Cikarang, qu\u1eadn Bekasi, mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y Java, Indonesia). Trong khi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Patriot (c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c Bekasi). C\u0169ng theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, hai tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1 l\u00fac 16h00, c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal \u0111\u00e1 l\u00fac 19h00.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c n\u1eefa \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n 8 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf hai b\u1ea3ng D, F thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu) tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00ean l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp, l\u00e0m quen s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm s\u00e2n ph\u1ee5 t\u1eadp c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 8 \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch c\u0169, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 11/8. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm h\u01a1n 1 ng\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh s\u1edbm 1 ng\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 g\u1eb7p Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4949","checkdouble":"192501"},{"date":"22:31 01/08","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/trung-ve-bui-tien-dung-he-lo-ve-phuong-phap-ren-quan-loi-hai-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 m\u00e0 anh kh\u00e1 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eafc t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PVF. Nh\u00ecn chung t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/854_dmhl1694-15331285268411369056055.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u2018n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng\u2019 v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p khi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 m\u00e0 anh kh\u00e1 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eafc t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB Viettel n\u00f3i: \"Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u1ea7y Park \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Th\u1ea7y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ec1 ra. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kho\u1ea3ng hai ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp trung, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea7n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, t\u1ea1o ra c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, c\u00f2n khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n th\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 tin\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Palestine tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 Asiad. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Palestine s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 3/8 t\u1edbi. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4948","checkdouble":"192502"},{"date":"23:25 01/08","title":"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/30/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t, vi\u1ec7c VTV th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3i khen.</h2><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM d\u00e0nh cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang gia t\u0103ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng &lsquo;h\u00e9t gi\u00e1&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e9p VTV ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n World Cup v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin VTV kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AISAD 2018 v\u00ec chi ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 cao. Vi\u1ec7c b\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/ve-xem-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-re-bat-ngo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ASIAD, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft VTV c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i AFF Cup 2018, v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la. T\u1ef1u chung nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh BLV Quang Huy c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao cho \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu. Do \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1, gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t hot. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd tr\u1edf \u0111i, ta c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nhanh l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u00e9p gi\u00e1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y VTV \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p, d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>V\u1eabn c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem ASIAD?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ASIAD 2018 tung ra, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi 99% VTV s\u1ebd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n k\u1ef3 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 18 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 VTV ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &quot;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0ng&quot; v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.&nbsp;Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1edb, VTV t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u00ec chi ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 cao, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady t\u1edbi ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a hai t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Viettel v\u00e0 Vingroup, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VTV\" title=\"VTV\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/anh_wc2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VTV kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecf ra h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV c\u0169ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu b\u00ean b\u00e1n l\u00e0 KJSMWORLD CORP ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VTV chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a VTV l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, VTV v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hay kh\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VTV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1eebng l\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u00ean b\u00e1n ch\u1ecbu gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1, ho\u1eb7c VTV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 'm\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n' \u0111\u1ee9ng sau t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, chuy\u1ec7n mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd &lsquo;ngh\u1ec9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rsquo; m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao - v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean&rsquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng, sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\">Sau ASIAD, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup</span><br>\r\nSau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup v\u00ec m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\">VTV tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 do ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t cao khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4947","checkdouble":"192504"},{"date":"18:02 01/08","title":"Roma t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i coi Malcom kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/roma-tuc-toi-coi-malcom-khong-ton-tai-tren-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng nay, CLB AS Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom v\u00e0 coi nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRoma v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00ec b\u1ecb l\u1eadt k\u00e8o<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 tai ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Malcom. Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ecdi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, anh (v\u00e0 Bordeaux) quay ngo\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Barca, khi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Roma v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n bay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Malcom \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Roma, khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng d\u1eady s\u00f3ng, cho r\u1eb1ng CLB Italia s\u1ebd&hellip; c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e9m g\u00e3y gi\u00f2 sao tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 cay c\u00fa xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter, khi Roma \u0111\u0103ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, trong \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef c\u1ee7a Malcom c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 26 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, v\u00e0 Barca ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb pha \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0103n m\u1eebng r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i cay c\u00fa, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i Barca 4-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom-180-192474.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Ernesto Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i Malcom</span> v\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb. Anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1edbi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y h\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a Malcom &ndash; HLV Di Francesco c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c khi b\u1ecb Barca c\u01b0\u1edbp h\u00e0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roma v\u1eabn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sao tr\u1ebb Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Barca 2-4 Roma</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/barca-2-4-roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\">Roma nh\u1eafn Barca: &ldquo;Mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf qua v\u1ee5 Malcom, v\u1eady \u0111\u01b0a Messi \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nCay c\u00fa xen l\u1eabn h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 cho n\u1ed7i nh\u1ee5c b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1edbp m\u1ea5t Malcom. Theo \u0111\u00f3, AS Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Barca nh\u1ea3 Messi cho h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom &ndash; Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4946","checkdouble":"192490"},{"date":"19:37 01/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8: Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-18-barca-bi-mat-dam-phan-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8.</h2><h2>Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18 Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18 Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/193541-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8: Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nT\u1edd  Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona \u0111ang t\u0103m tia si\u00eau sao Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a  Man United. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c  k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Eric Abidal c\u1ee7a Barca t\u1ea1i LA c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng  \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford nh\u01b0ng Man United v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh  tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n khi Pogba c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021.\r\n<h2>Giroud \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n Cobham. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a The Blues kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111ang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai khi Marseille \u0111ang b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Liverpool gia nh\u1eadp Sheffield United</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen Ben Woodburn \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Sheffield United theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 7, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho th\u1ea5y Woodburn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Sheffield United v\u00e0 Norwich. Nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Woodburn l\u00e0 s\u00e2n Bramall Lane.</div>\r\n<h2>Everton nh\u1eafm Rojo thay Yerry Mina</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Barcelona y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Yerry Mina. Ph\u00eda Everton kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed n\u00e0y v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m sang Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ph\u00eda Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed y\u00eau c\u1ea7u d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. V\u00e0 HLV Marco Silva \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<h2>MU nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 h\u1eadu Mourinho b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Zidane. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 ba d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Zidane l\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea3nh r\u1ed7i sau khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo-184-192440.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/8: Sao Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-317-mourinho-duoc-chieu-long-bang-2-bom-tan-184-192358.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7: Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng b\u1eb1ng 2 bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4945","checkdouble":"192496"},{"date":"19:57 01/08","title":"Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/2/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Mateo Kovacic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.</h2><h2>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kovacic c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kovacic t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng 3 n\u0103m \u1edf Real Madrid v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch danh gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i cho c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Inter c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 22.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Kovacic m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 37 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Marca, Mourinho bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Kovacic r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Bernabeu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid-172-189650.html\" target=\"_blank\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi cho Real</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 Kovacic mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i th\u00ec anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Man United. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi trung gian l\u00e0 Vlado Lemic \u0111\u1ebfn Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Kovacic. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-kho-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-172-192491.html\">V\u00ec sao MU kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-18-barca-bi-mat-dam-phan-pogba-184-192496.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8: Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4944","checkdouble":"192497"},{"date":"20:41 01/08","title":"Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/barca-bat-ngo-bi-mat-dam-phan-chieu-mo-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Rafinha v\u00e0 Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Aaron Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal hay Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Bi-mat-dam-phan,-Barca-muon-mua-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ri\u00eang c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pogba t\u1edbi Camp Nou. Abidal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Pogba m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf M.U, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u01b0a th\u00edch.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pogba Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/mourinho-muon-tay-pogba-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-nay-trong-he-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u00f2i 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Pogba\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi M.U, song Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa\u00a0c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2021, b\u1edfi v\u1eady mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba, Barca ph\u1ea3i chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U b\u1ecf ra 89.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Pogba</span>, Real c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 M.U \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat lui.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Pogba \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4943","checkdouble":"192489"},{"date":"21:40 01/08","title":"Arsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/4EC04E8E00000578-6016759-image-m-71_1533159211254.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u00cdt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 song Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau khi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f2n Cech ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Loftus-Cheek n\u00ean th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Emery.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: ARSENAL 1-1 (PEN 6-5) CHELSEA\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf HLV t\u1ea1i Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 th\u00e1ng.  Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi\u1ebfn  Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c. \u00d4ng gi\u00fap Arsenal ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c v\u1ecb  tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhau r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, bi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1eafn  r\u1ecfi, gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u  t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u1edf h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngay t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i  nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1 n\u1ebfp sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u0169. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Wenger th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf trong v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f3ng  k\u00edn c\u1eeda, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi trao c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd. Trong khi  \u0111\u00f3, HLV Emery t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ecdi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00d4ng \u0103n c\u00f9ng, t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi giao ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra  s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t  bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 gia t\u0103ng t\u00ednh k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u  th\u1ee7 Arsenal khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1edd \u0103n tr\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i hay c\u00e1c  thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed kh\u00e1c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0103n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i 1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EC04E8E00000578-6016759-image-m-71_1533159211254.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTh\u1ebf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n bao tr\u00f9m Arsenal. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ef1 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n, g\u1ea7n  g\u0169i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra cho h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao  h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Emile  Smith-Rowe \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean  \u0111\u1ea5t Singapore. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi  Chelsea, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u PSG v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. V\u00ec  th\u1ebf m\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n nay HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba  qua, c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alexandre Lacazette v\u00e0 Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t sung  m\u00e3n, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt  tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ea1i Nga. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c  m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Eden Hazard, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a  Chelsea tr\u1edf n\u00ean thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn  Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh London phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ICC 2018 n\u00e0y, HLV Emery kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 c\u1eb7p  Lacazette vs Aubameyang tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1eafm m\u1ed7i Aubameyang n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u.  H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon l\u00e0 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00f9a  tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Ozil c\u00f9ng Mkhitaryan. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 do t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb kh\u00e1  n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua Emile Smith-Rowe (thay Ramsey d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n  th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng), Elneny c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n binh Matteo Guendouzi. T\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng  ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c: trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis  Papastathopoulos.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea\" title=\"Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EBFF60200000578-0-image-a-11_1533152160836.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rudiger m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>B\u00ean ph\u00eda Chelsea, HLV Sarri - m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i CLB n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Premier  League n\u00f3i chung gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn - v\u1eabn gi\u1eef quan \u0111i\u1ec3m  \"1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng n\u00ean c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u  nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 Chelsea b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch cho c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. \u1ea4y th\u1ebf m\u00e0  so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Inter Milan tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i h\u00f4m c\u0169ng t\u1ea1i  ICC 2018, danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a The Blues ch\u1ec9 thay \u0111\u00fang 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m \u1edf h\u1ec7  th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1: Caballero thay \u0111\u00e0n em Bucka \u1edf khung g\u1ed7, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c  Rudiger th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Ampadu v\u00e0 Azpilicueta tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i thay  Zappacosta.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0  g\u1eafn k\u1ebft cao cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat  th\u1ee9 5. Sau khi Petr Cech - th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh danh \u1edf The Blues - t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u00fa ra  ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Fabregas, Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh F4 \u0111\u00e3 treo b\u00f3ng  cho trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi CLB l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m Chelsea ch\u01a1i h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n v\u00e0 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Arsenal. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 14,  \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o xanh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho r\u1eb1ng Bellerin ph\u1ea1m  l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Hudson-Odoi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 2000. Song \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc thay, Morata l\u1ea1i  kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Petr Cech tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Ph\u00fat 24, v\u1eabn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  \u0111\u00e0n em Hudson-Odoi trao m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c  n\u1ed5i Cech trong pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1, Arsenal ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n  Chelsea. Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 32, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong  tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ozil \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng cho Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Armenia c\u0103ng ngang nguy  hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0ng Aubameyang \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ee5t khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n ch\u01b0a  \u0111\u1ea7y 5m.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Arsenal tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 28 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EC0406F00000578-6016759-image-a-43_1533157720105.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lacazette g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Arsenal v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, Arsenal ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng ph\u00fat  41, ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cech khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Hudson-Odoi trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng  \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Emery m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9  gi\u1ea3i lao, Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp  c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m tung  m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p>Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m nguy. Ph\u00fat  57, v\u1eabn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t  d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c. C\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 theo  \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi Sarri th\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t  kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Emery th\u00ec h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 75, Lacazette m\u1edbi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 ngo\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Christensen  trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Chelsea r\u1ed3i s\u00fat ch\u00ecm v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i.  Ph\u00fat 84, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t l\u00e0m ng\u01a1 v\u1edbi Arsenal khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bulka  \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Iwobi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/4EBFEC3B00000578-6016759-image-a-15_1533153515715.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cech \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, d\u00e0n  \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i c\u00f2i  k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Arsenal m\u1edbi g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. Ozil c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \"l\u01b0\u1eddm rau g\u1eafp  th\u1ecbt\" qu\u00e1 hay cho Nelson v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i 18 \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng ngang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa v\u00f2ng  c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Lacazette \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>V\u1eady l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf ICC 2018, Chelsea l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m  lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Inter Milan \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang (c\u0169ng h\u00f2a 1-1  sau 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c). 5 lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat d\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai  \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m (Drinkwater, Abraham, Moses, Emerson, Lucas Piazon b\u00ean ph\u00eda  Chelsea v\u00e0 Lacazette, Nelson, Guendouzi, Maitland-Niles, Ozil b\u00ean ph\u00eda Arsenal)  song \u1edf lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat th\u1ee9 6 th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Petr Cech l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 trong tr\u1eadn  \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng 11m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Loftus-Cheek trong  khi Iwobi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho  Arsenal.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nARSENAL (4-3-3):</strong> Petr Cech; Hector Bellerin (Chambers 80'), Shkodran Mustafi, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Sead Kolasinac (Maitland-Niles 70'); Emile Smith-Rowe (Iwobi 63'), Mohamed Elneny, Matteo Guendouzi; Henrikh Mkhitaryan (Nelson 71'), Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang (Lacazette 71'), Mezut Ozil.<br>\r\n<strong>CHELSEA (4-3-3):</strong> Willy Caballero (Bulka 78'); Cezar Azpilicueta (Zappacosta 63'), Antonio Rudiger (Ampadu 63'), David Luiz (Christensen 46'), Marcos Alonso (Emerson 63'); Jorginho (Loftus-Cheek 78'); Ross Barkley (Bakayoko 78'), Cesc Fabregas (Drinkwater 46'); Pedro (Moses 63'), Alvaro Morata (Abraham 63'), Callum Hudson-Odoi (Piazon 86').</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4942","checkdouble":"192499"},{"date":"22:29 01/08","title":"Pires d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/pires-du-doan-lacazette-se-toa-sang-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Robert Pires tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Lacazette s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng 20 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><h2>Lacazette ch\u01a1i ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i vai c\u1ee7a Lacazette sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 46.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates khi ghi b\u00e0n ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Premier League, gi\u00fap Arsenal l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 4-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Lacazette ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u00edt \u1ecfi h\u01a1n. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n trong 23 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n ti\u1ebfp theo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Lacazette l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 trong 9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<h2>Pires tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Lacazette\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pires tin Lacazette s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pires tin Lacazette s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/pires-du-doan-lacazette-se-toa-sang-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pires tin Lacazette s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng Lacazette v\u1eabn b\u1ecb b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Pires tin r\u1eb1ng Lacazette v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u Lacazette c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng, Pires chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang Bwin:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLacazette l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Arsenal. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15-20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Lacazette c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Emery v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 HLV d\u00e0nh cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chi-dong-y-de-hlv-unai-emery-mua-nzonzi-neu-172-192467.html\">Arsenal ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Unai Emery mua Nzonzi n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\">Chelsea th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c, c\u00e2u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4941","checkdouble":"192500"},{"date":"23:17 01/08","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean Everton tr\u00e1nh xa trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng h\u1edb gi\u00e1 cao.</h2><h2>Everton ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Rojo\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 Everton mua Rojo Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 Everton mua Rojo Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rojo thay Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 Rojo n\u1ed5i l\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV Marco Silva \u01b0u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Man United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng Man United v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tham gia v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y sau khi b\u1ecb Barca kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Yerry Mina. The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Catalonia v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rojo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u00ean gia Ross Dyer c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0i ESPN kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec v\u1edbi tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMarcos Rojo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Everton l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec Man United c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Rojo t\u1edbi Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u01b0? T\u00f4i s\u1ebd khuy\u00ean h\u1ecd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng. Tr\u00e1nh th\u1eadt xa th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ra\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi anh. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Everton\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nRojo \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 107 l\u1ea7n cho Man United tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Sporting Lisbon n\u0103m 2014. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Rojo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-chap-nhan-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-neu-172-192428.html\">Everton ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-172-192398.html\">Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4940","checkdouble":"192503"},{"date":"06:02 02/08","title":"\u0110\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra tung t\u00edch c\u1ee7a sao M.U bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/sao-mu-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-mat-tich-nhung-ngay-qua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Martial bi\u1ec7t t\u00edch v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Anthony Martial xin ph\u00e9p tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu con trai. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ph\u00e9p, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Man United khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Martial quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi M.U h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi kh\u00f4ng quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang h\u1eb9n. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/sao-mu-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-mat-tich-nhung-ngay-qua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Martial h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Anthony Martial c\u00f3 em b\u00e9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb sau khi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh kh\u1ecfe, xinh \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y ngay nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi h\u00f4m qua, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup, Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 c\u00f2n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn \u0111ang x\u00f4n xao, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, con g\u00e1i m\u1edbi xinh c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng sau khi sinh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 trong tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial\" title=\"Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. &ldquo;C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Swan b\u00e9 nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb9, lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ed5 t\u00e2m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u01a1n Ch\u00faa c\u00f4 \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n&rdquo;, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Twitter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Xin l\u1ed7i nh\u01b0ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u&hellip; Ng\u00e0y mai, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial t\u1ea1i M.U v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho&hellip; Martial</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tien-dao-martial-khoe-anh-con-trai-moi-chao-doi-188-192135.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Martial khoe \u1ea3nh con trai m\u1edbi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-perisic-thay-martial-172-192116.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/martial-bo-do-du-dau-cua-mu-de-cham-vo-sinh-con-188-192079.html\">Martial b\u1ecf d\u1edf du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m v\u1ee3 sinh con</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4939","checkdouble":"192506"}]}